      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="获取豆瓣电视剧信息"><a href="#获取豆瓣电视剧信息" class="headerlink" title="获取豆瓣电视剧信息"></a>获取豆瓣电视剧信息</h1><h2 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h2><p>输入<strong>电视剧类型</strong>（美剧，英剧，韩剧，日剧，港剧，国产剧，日本动画）、<strong>排名方法</strong>（推荐，时间，评分）、欲输出的<strong>数目</strong>，即可得到所需信息。</p>
<h2 id="code"><a href="#code" class="headerlink" title="code"></a>code</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div><div class="line">89</div><div class="line">90</div><div class="line">91</div><div class="line">92</div><div class="line">93</div><div class="line">94</div><div class="line">95</div><div class="line">96</div><div class="line">97</div><div class="line">98</div><div class="line">99</div><div class="line">100</div><div class="line">101</div><div class="line">102</div><div class="line">103</div><div class="line">104</div><div class="line">105</div><div class="line">106</div><div class="line">107</div><div class="line">108</div><div class="line">109</div><div class="line">110</div><div class="line">111</div><div class="line">112</div><div class="line">113</div><div class="line">114</div><div class="line">115</div><div class="line">116</div><div class="line">117</div><div class="line">118</div><div class="line">119</div><div class="line">120</div><div class="line">121</div><div class="line">122</div><div class="line">123</div><div class="line">124</div><div class="line">125</div><div class="line">126</div><div class="line">127</div><div class="line">128</div><div class="line">129</div><div class="line">130</div><div class="line">131</div><div class="line">132</div><div class="line">133</div><div class="line">134</div><div class="line">135</div><div class="line">136</div><div class="line">137</div><div class="line">138</div><div class="line">139</div><div class="line">140</div><div class="line">141</div><div class="line">142</div><div class="line">143</div><div class="line">144</div><div class="line">145</div><div class="line">146</div><div class="line">147</div><div class="line">148</div><div class="line">149</div><div class="line">150</div><div class="line">151</div><div class="line">152</div><div class="line">153</div><div class="line">154</div><div class="line">155</div><div class="line">156</div><div class="line">157</div><div class="line">158</div><div class="line">159</div><div class="line">160</div><div class="line">161</div><div class="line">162</div><div class="line">163</div><div class="line">164</div><div class="line">165</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># coding: utf-8</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> selenium <span class="keyword">import</span> webdriver</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> selenium.common.exceptions <span class="keyword">import</span> NoSuchElementException</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> selenium.webdriver.support.ui <span class="keyword">import</span> WebDriverWait</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> selenium.webdriver.support <span class="keyword">import</span> expected_conditions <span class="keyword">as</span> EC</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> selenium.webdriver.common.by <span class="keyword">import</span> By</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> csv</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#打开初始页面，得到当前窗口句柄</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_initial_driver</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    driver = webdriver.Chrome()</div><div class="line">    driver.get(url)</div><div class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">3</span>)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">global</span> gen_win_handle</div><div class="line">    gen_win_handle = driver.current_window_handle</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> driver</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#点开电影详情页，保存所需信息，写入csv文件。</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">save_single_data</span><span class="params">(driver)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    elems = driver.find_elements_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//a[@class="item"]/p'</span>)</div><div class="line">    elems[i<span class="number">-1</span>].click()</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment"># 由主窗口切换至详情窗口</span></div><div class="line">    handles = driver.window_handles</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> each_handle <span class="keyword">in</span> handles:</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> each_handle == gen_win_handle:</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</div><div class="line">            driver.switch_to_window(each_handle)</div><div class="line">            <span class="comment"># 获取所需信息</span></div><div class="line">            film_name = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//h1/span[1]'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            Date = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//h1/span[2]'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            pat = re.compile(<span class="string">r'\d&#123;4&#125;'</span>)</div><div class="line">            release_year = re.search(pat, Date).group()  <span class="comment"># 利用正则将年份包含的括号去除</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span>:</div><div class="line">                director = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//div[@id="info"]/span[1]/span[2]'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">except</span> NoSuchElementException, e:</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">print</span> e.message</div><div class="line">                director = <span class="string">'No director found'</span></div><div class="line">            genres = driver.find_elements_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//div[@id="info"]/span[@property="v:genre"]'</span>)</div><div class="line">            genre = get_genre(genres)</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span>:</div><div class="line">                bref_intr = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//span[@property="v:summary"]'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">except</span> NoSuchElementException, e:</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">print</span> e.message</div><div class="line">                bref_intr = <span class="string">'No introduction'</span></div><div class="line">            rating = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//strong[@class="ll rating_num"]'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            voter_num = driver.find_element_by_xpath(<span class="string">'//a[@class="rating_people"]/span'</span>).text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">            content_list = [film_name, release_year, director, genre, bref_intr, rating, voter_num]</div><div class="line">            save_in_csv(content_list)</div><div class="line">            driver.close()</div><div class="line">            driver.switch_to_window(gen_win_handle)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> driver</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#获取要求数目的电影详情</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">save_page_data</span><span class="params">(url)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">global</span> i  <span class="comment">#使i在函数内起作用，而且变化后的数值可以影响到函数外的部分</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> i &lt;= item_num:</div><div class="line">        final_driver = save_single_data(url)</div><div class="line">        i += <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> final_driver</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#初始化csv文件：清空并写入首行数据</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">init_data</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">'g:\coding\python\python2.x\douban\movie_data.csv'</span>, <span class="string">"w"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> fp:</div><div class="line">        fp.truncate()</div><div class="line">        init_row = [<span class="string">'名称'</span>, <span class="string">'日期'</span>, <span class="string">'导演'</span>, <span class="string">'类型'</span>, <span class="string">'简介'</span>, <span class="string">'评分'</span>, <span class="string">'参评人数'</span>]</div><div class="line">        writer = csv.writer(fp)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span>:</div><div class="line">            writer.writerow(init_row)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">finally</span>:</div><div class="line">            fp.close()</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#格式化输出‘类型’</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">get_genre</span><span class="params">(genres)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    genre = <span class="string">""</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> len(genres) == <span class="number">1</span>:</div><div class="line">        genre = genres[<span class="number">0</span>].text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> gen <span class="keyword">in</span> genres:</div><div class="line">            genre = genre+<span class="string">'/'</span>+gen.text.encode(<span class="string">'utf-8'</span>)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> genre</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#将信息写入csv文件</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">save_in_csv</span><span class="params">(c_list)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">'g:\coding\python\python2.x\douban\movie_data.csv'</span>, <span class="string">'a+'</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> fp:</div><div class="line">        writer = csv.writer(fp)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span>:</div><div class="line">            writer.writerow(c_list)</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">finally</span>:</div><div class="line">            fp.close()</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#显式等待，待“更多”按钮加载出来后才开始后续</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">wait_page</span><span class="params">(driver)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    WebDriverWait(driver, <span class="number">5</span>).until(EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.CLASS_NAME, <span class="string">"more"</span>)))</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> driver</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#输入检查（未完成）</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">check_input_type</span><span class="params">(prompt)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">global</span> input_item</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span>:</div><div class="line">        input_item = input(prompt)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">except</span> NameError <span class="keyword">or</span> TypeError:</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> isinstance(input_item, int):</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> input_item</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</div><div class="line">            input_item = input(<span class="string">"number needed,other type won't work,enter again:"</span>)</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> input_item</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">tag_prompt = <span class="string">'Choose the tag of TV:\n1.Am_TV\n2.Br_TV\n3.Kr_TV\n4.Jp_TV\n5.Ch_TV\n6.HK_TV\n7.Jp_amination\nYour choice：'</span></div><div class="line">sort_prompt = <span class="string">'Choose the way of sorting TV:\n1.recommend\n2.time\n3.rank\nYour choice:'</span></div><div class="line">item_num_prompt = <span class="string">'How many TVs do you wanna show:'</span></div><div class="line">tag_no = check_input_type(tag_prompt)</div><div class="line">sort_no = check_input_type(sort_prompt)</div><div class="line">item_num = check_input_type(item_num_prompt)</div><div class="line">tags = [<span class="string">'%E7%BE%8E%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E8%8B%B1%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E9%9F%A9%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E6%97%A5%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%A7%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E6%B8%AF%E5%89%A7'</span>,</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">'%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB'</span>]</div><div class="line">sorts = [<span class="string">'recommend'</span>, <span class="string">'time'</span>, <span class="string">'rank'</span>]</div><div class="line">initial_url = <span class="string">'https://movie.douban.com/tv/#!type=tv&amp;tag=%s&amp;sort=%s&amp;page_limit=20&amp;page_start=0'</span> % (tags[tag_no<span class="number">-1</span>], sorts[sort_no<span class="number">-1</span>])</div><div class="line">loop_times = item_num/<span class="number">20</span></div><div class="line">count = <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">global</span> i</div><div class="line">i = <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">init_data()</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#三种情况，依据是否点击及点击多少次“更多”按钮分类</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> loop_times == <span class="number">0</span>:</div><div class="line">    driver = get_initial_driver(initial_url)</div><div class="line">    wait_page(driver)</div><div class="line">    a = save_page_data(driver)</div><div class="line">    a.quit()</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">elif</span> loop_times != <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> item_num % <span class="number">20</span> == <span class="number">0</span>:</div><div class="line">    driver = get_initial_driver(initial_url)</div><div class="line">    wait_page(driver)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> count &lt; loop_times:</div><div class="line">        more_button = driver.find_element_by_class_name(<span class="string">"more"</span>)</div><div class="line">        more_button.click()</div><div class="line">        count += <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    a = save_page_data(driver)</div><div class="line">    a.quit()</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</div><div class="line">    driver = get_initial_driver(initial_url)</div><div class="line">    wait_page(driver)</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> count &lt;= loop_times:</div><div class="line">        more_button = driver.find_element_by_class_name(<span class="string">"more"</span>)</div><div class="line">        more_button.click()</div><div class="line">        count += <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line">    a = save_page_data(driver)</div><div class="line">    a.quit()</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="学习内容"><a href="#学习内容" class="headerlink" title="学习内容"></a>学习内容</h2><ul>
<li>使用selenium自动化浏览器，模拟其操作实现动态网页（及包含<em>javascript</em>）的抓取，包括<strong>元素选取</strong>，<strong>点击按钮</strong>，<strong>设置等待</strong>。</li>
<li>使用selenium选择页面元素是采用了<code>find_element_by_xpath</code>方法，初步学习了下path语法。</li>
<li>使用了<em>headless</em>浏览器<em>PhantomJS</em>代替<em>Chrome</em>。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="注意事项及其他"><a href="#注意事项及其他" class="headerlink" title="注意事项及其他"></a>注意事项及其他</h2><ul>
<li>编码问题，勿对<em>str</em>进行<em>encode</em>，勿对<em>unicode</em>进行<em>decode</em>。</li>
<li>调用<em>Chrome</em>需使用<em>ChromeDriver</em>，在调用<em>Chrome</em>及<em>PhantomJS</em>时需将其添加至系统环境变量，若不添加，则在调用时需写明路径。</li>
<li>在抓取某些在部分电影存在，而在其他电影未必存在的信息，需采用异常处理机制，若检查出不存在，则需要用其他信息替换。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="问题及不足"><a href="#问题及不足" class="headerlink" title="问题及不足"></a>问题及不足</h2><ul>
<li>excel读取csv文件时易出现乱码，考虑改还信息存储方式（如使用MySQL）</li>
<li>输入检查未编写完成，而且目前只能考虑检查输入类型是否正确（是否输入数字），应考虑到输入范围。</li>
<li>获取<strong>集数</strong>和<strong>季数</strong></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
